data.description: The best townhome buy in Maple Grove, Quick possession! Just move-in! Delightful walkout home that shines with pride! Vaulted main level that overlooks a quiet wooded pond!  Stunning upgraded kitchen with stainless appliances, granite countertops, wood flooring, designer fixtures, pantry and main floor laundry. Sunny living room with sliding door to composite deck to enjoy the serene pond setting. The main level luxurious bedroom offers a walk-in closet. There is an upgraded ceramic bath with heated flooring. This home is nicely appointed in neutral tones throughout. The lower walkout level is nicely done with a family room, 2nd bedroom, ¾ ceramic bath (w/ heated flooring) and a mechanical/storage area. Walkout to a patio, with rollershade, to enjoy the sunsets. There is a double attached garage w/ opener. Located in a great complex, tucked away in a private hilltop neighborhood and convenient to all the amenities of Maple Grove. Walk or bike the trails along Elm Creek from your door!
